Redwood logs are received from cutting Redwood trees, which are found in the Woodcutting Guild or can be grown from a redwood sapling in the Farming Guild (with level 90 Farming). They require a Woodcutting level of 90 to chop and yield 380 Woodcutting experience per log.

Redwood logs can be burned with a Firemaking level of 90, giving 350 experience per log. They can also be fletched into 105 arrow shafts or a redwood shield, made into redwood pyre logs, used to make a redwood bird house, used to make a redwood fence in the Superior garden of a player-owned house, or used to light the abyssal lantern.
